## Istədiyimiz faylı oxumaq üçün istifadə olunur :

<?php
echo file_get_contents('/etc/passwd');
?>



## Əsas php file extensions:

.php - Standard PHP files.
.php3 - Older version of PHP files, used in PHP 3.
.php4 - Used for PHP 4 files.
.php5 - Used for PHP 5 files.
.phtml - PHP files that may contain HTML.
.phps - PHP source code files, usually for viewing source code.
.phar - PHP Archive files that can contain multiple PHP files and resources.
.php7 - Used for PHP 7 files.
